    <h2>Pricing</h2>

    <p>We charge a flat monthly fee for <b>unlimited usage</b>. In practice, that means you can have as many exhibits, species, and visitor page views as you like. Simply subscribe to the tier that best suits your needs, then configure your exhibits, add your species & unqique animals, then print out your QR codes and start using the platform straight away!
    <br><br><br>
    <b>Discover</b> – Give your visitors the ultimate experience by putting animal information right at their fingertips. Effortlessly enhance or replace your current exhibit signage with an engaging, modern solution that keeps them curious.
    <br><br>
    <b>Engage</b> – Bring your exhibits to life with a feature-packed digital guidebook. Delight visitors with stunning images, videos, audio guides, blogs, and quizzes. Showcase your team and send dynamic alerts for talks and feeds—all in one powerful platform.
    <br><br>
    <b>Accelerate</b> – Boost your revenue with in-app upsells for experiences, merchandise, and passes—or charge for Curious itself! Get rich analytics to track engagement and showcase top exhibits. Plus, impress visitors with a species finder that identifies animals from their photos.</p>
